node.text: We're at home with @chetnamakan, and today, she's sharing her recipe for flaky lachha paratha brushed with savory garlic butter. This simple dish is super easy to make but packs a ton of flavor from the carom seeds and garlic. Grab the recipe at the link in bio. #f52community

node.text: Founder of @iamcaribbeing Shelley Worrell (@shelleyworrell) is behind the bar cart showing us how to mix up extra-special cola drinks, featuring @fevertreemixers Cola. Not-Your-Typical Rum and Cola gets its upgrade from a splash of Champagne (see what we mean by extra-special?), while her Whiskey and Cola gets a lift from a dash of bitters and some fresh lime juice. Whichever you choose, each is bound to impress at your next happy hour. #f52partner

node.title: Not-Your-Typical Rum and Cola & Whiskey and Cola with Orange Bitters
